= sfSecurityManager plug-in =

The `sfSecurityManager` provide some new tasks to the symfony command line tool
  * symfony security-list : List all the security strategy for the project
  * symfony security-is-secure app [module] [action] on|off : Update the is_secure flag for an app (optional module and/or action)
  * symfony security-add-credential app [module] [action] on|off : Add a credential to an app (optional module and/or action)
  * symfony security-del-credential app [module] [action] on|off : Delete a credential to an app (optional module and/or action)


== Installation ==

  * Install the plug-in
  
    {{{
      symfony plugin-install http://plugins.symfony-project.com/sfSecurityManager
    }}}

  * Clear the cache

    {{{
      symfony cc
    }}}

  * You're done.

== Usage ==
 
    {{{
  $ ./symfony security-list
  admin :
    is_secure   : yes
    credentials : admin and webmaster
  process :
    is_secure   : no
  www :
    is_secure   : no
  
  $ ./symfony security-del-credential admin webmaster
  >> save      /usr/local/www/users/romain/sec...apps//admin/config/security.yml
  
  $ ./symfony security-list
  admin :
    is_secure   : yes
    credentials : admin
  process :
    is_secure   : no
  www :
    is_secure   : no
  
  $ ./symfony security-add-credential admin account list webmaster
  >> save      /usr/local/www/users/romain/sec...les/account/config/security.yml

  $ ./symfony security-is-secure admin account list on
  >> save      /usr/local/www/users/romain/sec...les/account/config/security.yml
  
  $ ./symfony security-list
  admin :
    is_secure   : yes
    credentials : admin
    account :
      list :
        is_secure   : on
        credentials : webmaster
  process :
    is_secure   : no
  www :
    is_secure   : no
    
  $ ./symfony security-is-secure admin account off
  >> save      /usr/local/www/users/romain/sec...les/account/config/security.yml
  
  $ ./symfony security-list
  admin :
    is_secure   : yes
    credentials : admin
    account :
      list :
        is_secure   : no
        credentials : webmaster
      all (default) :
        is_secure   : no
  process :
    is_secure   : no
  www :
    is_secure   : no
    }}}

